    #faq div {
        font-size: large;
    }
    #faq h2 button {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
</style>

<div id="menu" class="d-none col-md-3 menu d-md-block scroll"></div>

<section id="faq" class="offset-md-3 col-md-9 col-lg-6">
    <h2 class="my-4 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
  
    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
  
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading1">
          <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
            1. What is God In Prints (GIP)?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            God In Prints is a virtual library and knowledge repository that provides biographies, books, scriptures, articles, songs, and resources to support personal and spiritual growth—especially for Christians and faith seekers.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading2">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
            2. Is the content on GIP free to access?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes, all resources on GIP are available for free (or near-free) to ensure everyone can benefit from the platform, regardless of financial status.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading3">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
            3. What kind of resources can I find here?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            <ul>
              <li>Biographies of notable Christians</li>
              <li>Classic and modern Christian books</li>
              <li>Multi-version scriptures</li>
              <li>Articles on spiritual growth and godly living</li>
              <li>Inspirational songs and movies</li>
              <li>Tools for personal development and ministry support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading4">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
            4. How can I suggest a topic or contribute content?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading4" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Each document page includes a suggestion form where you can:
            <ul>
              <li>Recommend new topics or resources</li>
              <li>Submit articles, books, or biographies for review and possible inclusion</li>
            </ul>
            We welcome your contributions to help grow this repository!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading5">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
            5. Can I submit my own writings or materials to GIP?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading5" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes! You can use the post forms available on the site to submit your work. While we're working on a full admin portal for contributors, submissions via the form are reviewed and appreciated.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading6">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
            6. Do I need to create an account to access the content?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="heading6" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Yes, user account is required to access some materials on GIP, for personalized features and easier contributions.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
